HEADWORD: Ineffectualness
<hw>In`ef*fec"tu*al*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Lack of effect, or of
power to produce it; inefficacy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>ineffectualness</qex> of some men's devotion.</q>
<rj><qau>Wake.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ineffervescence</ent>⟦br⟧
